Study
The number of day of dedicated study to learn a new language depends on its difficulty relative to the languages you already now.
If the new language you want to learn is in the same language tree as a language you already now, then this language is considered to be an easy one for you, otherwise it's a hard language.
(See. <a class="internal-link" target="" data-note-icon="" href="/neldardhen-world/endea/cultures-nations/languages/languages/#b6cf64">Language Tree</a>)

