Working
Once you have decided on the job that you will be performing during the downtime period, select with your Storyteller the skill and attrivbute that would apply.
The Story teller will then give you an expected average amount and a difficulty.
Roll for each day of downtime (or week or month, if downtime is very long) and count your accumulated success.
The formula belove will give you the amount of money you managed to make during downtime.

